Name: Ji'nara
Description: First Ascendant of the Tal'darim. Ji'nara choosing this path specializes in casting spells from a distance, using her surging energy to destroy her enemies. **Can attack ground and air units**

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: Ji'nara sacrifices a nearby supplicant, fully restores the user's energy, and gain 1 stack of Power Overwhelming.
Root.Name: Sacrifice

Root.Tooltip:
Search target area for 1 second. Affected enemy units will have their movement speed greatly reduced and will fall into stasis after staying in the area for more than 0.5 seconds. The stasis lasts for 3 seconds.

If an enemy unit under the influence of Chains of Ji'nara, it will take 12 damage and fall into a even longer stasis, lasting 4.5 seconds.

Every time an enemy unit is killed by Chains of Ji'nara, the cooldown time of this skill will be reduced by 1 second.
Root.Name: Chains of Ji'nara

Root.Tooltip: Mark the target unit for 3 seconds. After the telekinesis ends, she will fire a beam to it, causing 12 damage. If the target is affected by Chains of Ji'nara, the damage will increased and it will spread Chains of Ji'nara to other units.
Root.Name: Scarlet Execution

Root.Tooltip:
Creates a phantom at the target location, replacing this skill with Scarlet Execution. After 1.3 seconds, Jinara will dash to the phantom's position.

Scarlet Execution: Mark the target unit. After the telekinesis ends, she will fire a beam to it, causing massive damage and spreading Chains of Ji'nara to other units.
Root.Name: Telekinesis

Root.Tooltip: Ji'nara aggregates the psionic power and acquires Soul Fire as her weapon. It cost 4 energy each second. Ji'nara's weapon damage to become spell damage, ignore target armor.
Root.Name: Enable Soul Burn

Root.Tooltip: Disable Soul Burn and stop depleting energy.
Root.Name: Disable Soul Burn

Root.Tooltip: Chant for 3 seconds and cause 120 damage to the enemy units in the target area. If the unit is affected by Chains of Ji'nara, it will take an additional 240 damage.
Root.Name: Requiem

Root.Tooltip: Sacrifice a Supplicant to gain 1 stack of Power Overwhelming. When stack number is below 10, each stack permanently gains 100 shields and 25% ability damage. When stack number is more than 10, each stack permanently gains 50 shields and 25% ability damage.
Root.Name: Unlimited Power!

Root.Tooltip: Sacrifice a Supplicant to gain 1 stack of Power Overwhelming. Each stack permanently gains 100 shields and 25% ability damage. Stacks up to 10 times.
Root.Name: Power Overwhelming

Root.Tooltip: Ji'nara converts 25% of spell damage into her own shields.
Root.Name: Psi Absorption

Root.Tooltip:
After Ji'nara uses Scarlet Execution to kill units affected by Chains of Ji'nara, it will generate 1 stack of "Frenzy". At 3 stacks, the next Chains of Ji'nara will summon an invincible "Scarlet Warden" lasting for 8 seconds.

Each time Ji'nara uses her skill, its duration can be extended, and it will mimic Jinara's skills, but only cause 10% damage. For every additional Watcher on the field, its damage will be increased by an additional 10%. The current damage is 0%.
Root.Name: Scarlet Warden

Root.Tooltip: Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
Root.Name: Set Rally Point

Behaviors.Tooltip: 25% of Ji'nara's damage is turned into her shields.
Behaviors.Name: Unyielding Soul
